00:07:11.102 --> 00:07:12.689
- your nose will stop flaring.
- Hey!

00:07:13.832 --> 00:07:15.452
You're talking nonsense.

00:07:30.199 --> 00:07:31.232
Chai.

00:07:35.309 --> 00:07:36.375
Chai.

00:07:39.350 --> 00:07:41.133
Lately, you haven't been talking to me,

00:07:41.158 --> 00:07:42.598
haven't been going anywhere with me,

00:07:42.986 --> 00:07:44.466
acting like we don't know each other.

00:07:44.612 --> 00:07:45.986
Do you hate me now?

00:08:03.893 --> 00:08:05.240
Why don't you tell me?

00:08:06.935 --> 00:08:08.796
How many hundred reasons do I need

00:08:09.356 --> 00:08:10.550
to hate you?

00:08:16.765 --> 00:08:17.765
Listen, Ek.

00:08:19.915 --> 00:08:21.382
No matter what it takes,

00:08:23.099 --> 00:08:24.321
I want to be with you.

00:08:25.341 --> 00:08:26.386
But now,

00:08:27.078 --> 00:08:28.398
give me some time.

00:08:30.034 --> 00:08:32.364
I'm going to make myself better,
to be worthy of you.

00:08:34.870 --> 00:08:36.089
So that we can be together.

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:40.941
So if I wait,

00:08:41.565 --> 00:08:42.839
we can be together, right?

00:08:45.865 --> 00:08:47.052
Yeah.

00:08:48.277 --> 00:08:50.581
So stop whining already.

00:08:51.381 --> 00:08:52.381
Okay?

00:08:52.515 --> 00:08:53.982
Okay.

00:08:55.813 --> 00:08:56.821
I'm going.

00:09:20.409 --> 00:09:23.342
Sorry for the wait.

00:09:23.988 --> 00:09:25.318
Thank you.

