Here are your noodles, ladies.

00:09:26.935 --> 00:09:28.007
Thank you.

00:09:28.032 --> 00:09:29.080
Enjoy your meal.

00:09:29.105 --> 00:09:30.234
Thank you.

00:09:32.193 --> 00:09:33.193
Here.

00:09:33.781 --> 00:09:34.835
Thank you.

