00:09:53.780 --> 00:09:55.233
Because I know you like it.

00:09:56.307 --> 00:09:58.269
I've never told anyone before.

00:09:59.277 --> 00:10:00.640
I could tell from how you always buy it

00:10:00.664 --> 00:10:02.466
to eat at the rehearsal room.

