Is it that obvious?

00:10:19.804 --> 00:10:21.647
When you eat something you like, Lin,

00:10:21.680 --> 00:10:23.208
you chewing, nom, nom.

00:10:23.232 --> 00:10:25.081
And you make this face. Look.

00:10:28.398 --> 00:10:29.668
Hey.

00:10:29.692 --> 00:10:31.019
That's not true.

00:10:31.232 --> 00:10:33.259
I don't look that ugly.

00:10:33.757 --> 00:10:35.061
Want to see the proof?

00:10:35.085 --> 00:10:36.792
I brought my Polaroid camera.

00:10:38.997 --> 00:10:40.552
