Bang, bang, bang, bang.

00:13:19.696 --> 00:13:20.696
Bang?

00:13:21.213 --> 00:13:22.380
What is "bang"?

00:13:22.547 --> 00:13:23.350
Very cool.

00:13:23.374 --> 00:13:24.469
Oh.

00:13:24.775 --> 00:13:25.998
Okay, very cool.

00:13:26.022 --> 00:13:27.113
Yeah, that's good.

