Oh, and who would do that?

00:13:53.558 --> 00:13:54.832
He's got so many jokes.

00:13:55.390 --> 00:13:56.390
Come here.

00:14:04.733 --> 00:14:05.902
So proud.

00:14:07.695 --> 00:14:08.304
Thank you.

