It's not the same.

00:16:59.457 --> 00:17:02.661
Don't compare my work with what you do.

00:17:05.205 --> 00:17:07.167
If you insist that it's about income,

00:17:08.367 --> 00:17:09.413
then how about this?

00:17:09.853 --> 00:17:11.388
